under the moonlight♪

574
00:29:00,112 --> 00:29:03,978
♪In this world, I want nothing but her♪

575
00:29:04,464 --> 00:29:06,064
♪Love in laughter, hate in silence♪

576
00:29:06,064 --> 00:29:08,880
♪My heart yearns
for a shining star like her♪

577
00:29:09,008 --> 00:29:13,136
♪She can write her story with my love♪

578
00:29:13,584 --> 00:29:15,146
♪Greedy dreams and beating heart♪

579
00:29:15,146 --> 00:29:17,738
♪Sword sings in the fierce wind♪

580
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:20,746
♪My heart lingers over a dream♪

581
00:29:21,616 --> 00:29:23,952
♪Chasing, wandering♪

582
00:29:23,952 --> 00:29:25,706
♪Zither and flute♪

583
00:29:26,224 --> 00:29:30,282
♪Always seeking each other's company♪

584
00:29:30,544 --> 00:29:32,528
♪Embrace a mortal's heart♪

585
00:29:32,528 --> 00:29:34,736
♪Cross the eternal river♪

586
00:29:35,024 --> 00:29:39,312
♪Guard the dawn light
in the darkest moment♪

587
00:29:39,344 --> 00:29:43,434
♪Settle the story of the life♪

588
00:29:43,696 --> 00:29:47,984
♪Slay the demon in my heart
with composure♪

589
00:29:47,984 --> 00:29:49,744
♪Embrace a mortal's heart♪

590
00:29:49,744 --> 00:29:52,266
♪Steer through this bumpy road♪

591
00:29:52,656 --> 00:29:56,816
♪Love often brings difficulties♪

592
00:29:58,627 --> 00:29:59,186
Great Emperor.

593
00:30:00,066 --> 00:30:00,747
Princess

594
00:30:00,867 --> 00:30:01,907
completed

595
00:30:02,186 --> 00:30:04,507
King of Chenrong's notes in three years.

596
00:30:05,186 --> 00:30:05,706
Aptitude.

597
00:30:05,867 --> 00:30:06,706
Talent.

598
00:30:06,907 --> 00:30:08,186
Hard work.

599
00:30:08,346 --> 00:30:09,547
Each one is indispensable.

600
00:30:10,147 --> 00:30:11,586
She's like her mother.

601
00:30:32,306 --> 00:30:32,907
Grandfather.

602
00:30:35,387 --> 00:30:36,186
You're back.

603
00:30:40,667 --> 00:30:41,907
Xiaoyao is back.

604
00:30:42,787 --> 00:30:45,426
Aren't you going to keep her company?

605
00:30:52,267 --> 00:30:53,466
Xiaoyao is busy.

606
00:30:53,552 --> 00:30:54,096
Great Emperor,

607
00:30:54,346 --> 00:30:55,066
after this game.

608
00:30:55,907 --> 00:30:56,826
I've just finished reading

609
00:30:56,826 --> 00:30:58,106
your combat notes

610
00:30:58,147 --> 00:30:59,106
and finally figured

611
00:30:59,106 --> 00:30:59,946
something out.

612
00:31:18,426 --> 00:31:19,024
Xiaoyao.

613
00:31:20,627 --> 00:31:21,547
Take a break.

614
00:31:22,106 --> 00:31:22,987
Just a bit more.

615
00:32:17,667 --> 00:32:18,346
Where is Xuan?

616
00:32:20,466 --> 00:32:21,106
Xiaoyao.

617
00:32:23,547 --> 00:32:24,826
I made your favorite dish.

618
00:32:26,416 --> 00:32:26,960
Did...

619
00:32:27,106 --> 00:32:28,226
Did you make this?

620
00:32:29,147 --> 00:32:29,747
Yeah.

621
00:32:30,787 --> 00:32:32,667
To reward you for your hard work.

622
00:32:41,747 --> 00:32:42,706
Grandfather.

623
00:32:43,027 --> 00:32:43,907
Fenglong.

624
00:32:44,426 --> 00:32:45,346
Food is ready.

625
00:32:45,872 --> 00:32:46,512
Okay.

626
00:32:46,907 --> 00:32:47,627
Coming.

627
00:32:49,387 --> 00:32:49,907
Grandfather.

628
00:32:50,426 --> 00:32:51,226
Let me think.

629
00:32:53,027 --> 00:32:53,706
Fenglong.

630
00:32:53,907 --> 00:32:54,667
Food is ready.

631
00:32:58,547 --> 00:33:00,226
I know you're good at seasoning,

632
00:33:01,466 --> 00:33:02,186
but try this.

633
00:33:02,747 --> 00:33:04,306
Try the folk cuisines I learned

634
00:33:04,346 --> 00:33:05,267
throughout Dahuang.

635
00:33:10,907 --> 00:33:11,472
Grandfather.

636
00:33:11,867 --> 00:33:12,987
This game of chess

637
00:33:13,147 --> 00:33:14,426
taught me so much.

638
00:33:14,787 --> 00:33:15,826
I've benefited a lot.

639
00:33:16,547 --> 00:33:18,547
Your strategies of attack and retreat

640
00:33:18,747 --> 00:33:20,507
were obtained
from the battlefield, right?

641
00:33:22,907 --> 00:33:23,507
Fenglong,

642
00:33:24,147 --> 00:33:25,547
even if you are not hungry,

643
00:33:26,547 --> 00:33:27,946
you should let Grandfather eat.

644
00:33:28,706 --> 00:33:29,547
It's rare for me

645
00:33:29,547 --> 00:33:30,507
to see Grandfather.

646
00:33:31,066 --> 00:33:31,867
Unlike you.

647
00:33:32,147 --> 00:33:33,507
You're always by his side

648
00:33:33,586 --> 00:33:34,507
to seek advice.

649
00:33:34,826 --> 00:33:35,346
Wait.

650
00:33:35,627 --> 00:33:36,747
Who says you can

651
00:33:37,387 --> 00:33:38,226
call him Grandfather?

652
00:33:38,507 --> 00:33:39,306
With your consent,

653
00:33:39,667 --> 00:33:41,186
I can address him like that.

654
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:46,224
Your Majesty.

655
00:33:47,387 --> 00:33:48,346
I want to marry Xiaoyao

656
00:33:48,826 --> 00:33:49,706
as soon as possible.

657
00:34:01,426 --> 00:34:02,667
This is the Lamp of Time.

658
00:34:03,027 --> 00:34:04,066
With life as the flame

659
00:34:04,226 --> 00:34:05,267
that sustains it.

660
00:34:06,306 --> 00:34:08,112
This is the Guifang Family's rare weapon.

661
00:34:08,307 --> 00:34:09,226
I've heard of it

662
00:34:09,226 --> 00:34:10,186
but never seen it.

663
00:34:10,768 --> 00:34:11,376
Uncle.

664
00:34:11,507 --> 00:34:12,466
How did you get it?

665
00:34:12,987 --> 00:34:15,307
Once the Lamp of Time is lit,

666
00:34:15,906 --> 00:34:17,987
it takes your hair as the wick,

667
00:34:18,626 --> 00:34:20,866
your blood as the oil,

668
00:34:21,347 --> 00:34:24,107
and your life as the flame.

669
00:34:24,987 --> 00:34:26,426
Are you really ready for this?

670
00:34:29,226 --> 00:34:29,946
I'm ready.

671
00:34:30,386 --> 00:34:30,987
Jing.

672
00:34:31,226 --> 00:34:32,307
Is this truly worth it?

673
00:34:32,706 --> 00:34:33,987
You're the chief of Tushan Family.

674
00:34:34,107 --> 00:34:34,787
Your family,

675
00:34:34,946 --> 00:34:35,507
fame, fortune,

676
00:34:35,547 --> 00:34:36,107
power,

677
00:34:36,267 --> 00:34:37,226
and all the splendors.

678
00:34:37,226 --> 00:34:38,547
Won't you hold onto any of those?

679
00:34:38,787 --> 00:34:39,906
Do you have to risk your life?

680
00:34:40,706 --> 00:34:41,787
I'm not risking my life.

681
00:34:42,946 --> 00:34:44,307
Xiaoyao is my life.

682
00:34:46,226 --> 00:34:47,787
I'm not like you and Fenglong.

683
00:34:48,706 --> 00:34:49,787
My heart is too small

684
00:34:50,587 --> 00:34:51,866
to hold the entire world.

685
00:34:52,906 --> 00:34:54,107
It can only hold one person.

686
00:34:57,027 --> 00:34:58,186
Please begin, Uncle.

687
00:35:37,067 --> 00:35:37,866
Beggar.

688
00:35:38,067 --> 00:35:39,146
Starting today,

689
00:35:39,347 --> 00:35:40,307
you'll be Ye Shiqi.

690
00:35:42,747 --> 00:35:43,587
Don't follow me.

691
00:35:55,226 --> 00:35:55,866
Jing.

692
00:36:00,787 --> 00:36:01,466
Jing.

693
00:36:01,946 --> 00:36:02,587
Jing.

694
00:36:02,987 --> 00:36:03,626
Jing.

695
00:36:05,107 --> 00:36:05,827
Uncle.

696
00:36:30,866 --> 00:36:31,466
Great Emperor.

697
00:36:32,466 --> 00:36:34,386
I think Xiaoyao and I
should hold the wedding.

698
00:36:35,386 --> 00:36:36,307
My grandfather

699
00:36:36,307 --> 00:36:37,466
is waiting for a great-grandson.

700
00:36:37,906 --> 00:36:39,347
I bet you're anticipating, too.

701
00:36:40,186 --> 00:36:41,027
It's fine by me.

702
00:36:41,946 --> 00:36:43,987
As for the wedding,

703
00:36:44,347 --> 00:36:45,347
it's up to you.

704
00:36:47,547 --> 00:36:48,226
Your Majesty.

705
00:36:49,226 --> 00:36:50,307
You already have

706
00:36:50,386 --> 00:36:51,626
several consorts in Zijin Palace.

707
00:36:52,307 --> 00:36:53,787
Yet I am still all alone.

708
00:36:53,946 --> 00:36:54,866
So lonely.

709
00:36:55,466 --> 00:36:56,386
Your Majesty,

710
00:36:56,386 --> 00:36:57,626
won't you show me some pity?

711
00:37:06,146 --> 00:37:07,186
This is Xiaoyao's wedding.

712
00:37:07,747 --> 00:37:08,706
Why are you asking me?

713
00:37:11,827 --> 00:37:12,626
Xiaoyao.

714
00:37:13,547 --> 00:37:15,146
Would you like to hold the wedding soon?

715
00:37:24,507 --> 00:37:25,107
Xiaoyao.

716
00:37:26,067 --> 00:37:27,946
A wedding is just a formality.

717
00:37:28,906 --> 00:37:30,386
If you like Chenrong Mountain,

718
00:37:30,866 --> 00:37:32,787
we can ask His Majesty for a peak

719
00:37:33,267 --> 00:37:34,426
to settle down here.

720
00:37:34,866 --> 00:37:36,307
If you like Zhiyi,

721
00:37:36,747 --> 00:37:38,466
we can renovate the old residence

722
00:37:38,466 --> 00:37:39,386
of the Chishui Family

723
00:37:40,146 --> 00:37:41,347
and reside there.

724
00:37:42,027 --> 00:37:43,946
If you find both places too noisy,

725
00:37:44,146 --> 00:37:45,226
we can go to Chishui.

726
00:37:45,827 --> 00:37:47,027
You can open a clinic.

727
00:37:47,466 --> 00:37:48,386
I support you.

728
00:37:48,906 --> 00:37:49,747
You know me.

729
00:37:50,307 --> 00:37:51,787
I've always been mischievous,

730
00:37:52,267 --> 00:37:53,987
and have never been fond of formalities,

731
00:37:54,226 --> 00:37:55,386
or bound by norms.

732
00:37:55,906 --> 00:37:57,507
No matter what you want to do,

733
00:37:58,466 --> 00:37:59,307
I'm happy

734
00:37:59,426 --> 00:38:00,347
as long as you're happy.

735
00:38:04,027 --> 00:38:04,666
Xiaoyao...

736
00:38:04,666 --> 00:38:05,987
If Xiaoyao agrees,

737
00:38:06,787 --> 00:38:08,107
then it's settled.

738
00:38:11,386 --> 00:38:12,067
You've agreed?

739
00:38:17,466 --> 00:38:19,312
Thank you, Your Majesty.
Thank you, Great Emperor.

740
00:38:19,946 --> 00:38:21,347
I'll ask my grandfather to send someone

741
00:38:21,626 --> 00:38:23,307
to Haoling to settle the wedding date.

742
00:38:32,106 --> 00:38:36,192
♪You appear at the end of the river♪

743
00:38:36,538 --> 00:38:40,464
♪But disappear as clouds rise♪

744
00:38:40,890 --> 00:38:44,976
♪You appear when I look up♪

745
00:38:45,210 --> 00:38:49,136
♪But disappear as I lower my head♪

746
00:38:49,616 --> 00:38:53,712
♪You appear in the snow♪

747
00:38:53,792 --> 00:38:57,893
♪But disappear as flowers bloom♪

748
00:38:58,240 --> 00:39:00,880
♪You appear as the smoke rises♪

749
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:06,480
♪You disappear in the light♪

750
00:39:15,120 --> 00:39:15,706
Uncle.

751
00:39:15,827 --> 00:39:16,587
How is he?

752
00:39:19,307 --> 00:39:20,787
His heart meridian is damaged.

753
00:39:20,946 --> 00:39:22,787
But fortunately, he survived.

754
00:39:24,906 --> 00:39:26,866
You were half dead once.

755
00:39:27,666 --> 00:39:29,827
Rest well after you return.

756
00:39:30,226 --> 00:39:31,347
You must not

757
00:39:31,347 --> 00:39:32,587
exhaust yourself

758
00:39:33,466 --> 00:39:34,987
or overthink again.

759
00:39:40,027 --> 00:39:40,987
Uncle, are you okay?

760
00:39:41,507 --> 00:39:43,866
I've just overexerted my spirit power.

761
00:39:44,946 --> 00:39:46,626
I'll be fine after a nap.

762
00:39:58,547 --> 00:39:59,226
Jing.

763
00:40:00,186 --> 00:40:01,267
Do you remember something?

764
00:40:12,747 --> 00:40:13,507
And after that?

765
00:40:14,507 --> 00:40:15,466
After that,

766
00:40:16,386 --> 00:40:18,027
I don't remember anything.

767
00:40:18,587 --> 00:40:19,787
The same outcome.

768
00:40:20,386 --> 00:40:22,347
Fangfeng Yiying is really ruthless.

769
00:40:22,507 --> 00:40:23,866
She actually lowered herself

770
00:40:23,866 --> 00:40:24,626
and shamelessly

771
00:40:24,747 --> 00:40:26,386
seduced you
in the form of another woman.

772
00:40:26,987 --> 00:40:27,547
Jing.

773
00:40:29,906 --> 00:40:31,267
Although it's not your fault,

774
00:40:31,587 --> 00:40:32,747
at this point,

775
00:40:34,547 --> 00:40:35,827
you might as well give up.

776
00:40:36,146 --> 00:40:37,547
A broken heart is hard to heal.

777
00:40:37,787 --> 00:40:38,827
My uncle said

778
00:40:38,827 --> 00:40:40,067
that you should rest well

779
00:40:40,507 --> 00:40:42,267
and avoid overthinking things.

780
00:40:42,587 --> 00:40:44,386
Otherwise, your life will be in danger.

781
00:40:49,347 --> 00:40:50,067
Xiaoyao.

782
00:40:51,267 --> 00:40:52,466
Have you really decided?

783
00:40:56,307 --> 00:40:57,587
The wedding will take place

784
00:40:57,946 --> 00:40:59,027
sooner or later anyway

785
00:40:59,347 --> 00:41:00,987
and Fenglong wants it done soon.

786
00:41:01,426 --> 00:41:02,466
Then I will ask Father

787
00:41:03,107 --> 00:41:04,067
to choose a wedding date.

788
00:41:05,347 --> 00:41:06,226
Fenglong mentioned it

789
00:41:06,226 --> 00:41:07,626
and you just decided on it.

790
00:41:08,426 --> 00:41:10,027
You haven't thought it through.

791
00:41:10,547 --> 00:41:11,987
Isn't it a bit hasty?

792
00:41:13,827 --> 00:41:15,507
I've known Fenglong for decades.

793
00:41:15,626 --> 00:41:17,626
We know each other very well.

794
00:41:18,547 --> 00:41:19,587
There's nothing hasty.

795
00:41:30,146 --> 00:41:30,987
Xuan.

796
00:41:32,906 --> 00:41:34,307
I don't want you to get married.

797
00:41:34,787 --> 00:41:35,706
I understand

798
00:41:35,946 --> 00:41:36,827
how you feel.

799
00:41:38,226 --> 00:41:40,267
Back when you married Xinyue,

800
00:41:41,027 --> 00:41:42,507
I also felt hurt deep down.

801
00:41:43,866 --> 00:41:45,747
I felt that she would take you away

802
00:41:46,107 --> 00:41:49,027
and I would become an outsider.

803
00:41:50,987 --> 00:41:53,747
You were upset when I got married?

804
00:41:56,507 --> 00:41:58,186
I was very upset.

805
00:41:59,347 --> 00:42:00,747
It was like something

806
00:42:02,146 --> 00:42:03,587
that belonged to me was taken away.

807
00:42:04,107 --> 00:42:04,688
Xiaoyao.

808
00:42:06,787 --> 00:42:08,827
But then I realized I was being petty.

809
00:42:09,267 --> 00:42:11,027
You have been married to Xinyue
for so long,

810
00:42:11,267 --> 00:42:12,347
yet you are still my brother

811
00:42:12,706 --> 00:42:13,946
and so nice to me.

812
00:42:14,186 --> 00:42:15,386
Xinyue didn't take you away.

813
00:42:16,307 --> 00:42:17,347
Don't worry, Xuan.

814
00:42:17,507 --> 00:42:18,987
After I marry Fenglong,

815
00:42:19,186 --> 00:42:20,626
you'll still be my closest family member

816
00:42:20,906 --> 00:42:22,027
whom I trust the most.

817
00:42:22,466 --> 00:42:23,347
Your closest family member

818
00:42:24,666 --> 00:42:25,787
whom you trust the most.

819
00:42:27,466 --> 00:42:28,547
Aren't you?

820
00:42:28,747 --> 00:42:29,426
Xiaoyao.

821
00:42:30,307 --> 00:42:31,866
I don't want you to leave. I want...

822
00:42:31,866 --> 00:42:32,866
Cang Xuan, let go.

823
00:42:41,747 --> 00:42:42,267
Xuan.

824
00:42:43,747 --> 00:42:44,547
Let it go.

825
00:42:44,866 --> 00:42:47,146
We can't let
the Chishui Family beat us to it

826
00:42:47,507 --> 00:42:48,347
and make Father feel

827
00:42:48,347 --> 00:42:49,827
that he has to learn about

828
00:42:50,027 --> 00:42:51,787
my wedding from someone else.

829
00:43:19,098 --> 00:43:22,330
♪Looking back on my old days♪

830
00:43:23,616 --> 00:43:27,898
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

831
00:43:29,978 --> 00:43:34,778
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

832
00:43:37,914 --> 00:43:40,186
♪Only emptiness remained♪

833
00:43:43,130 --> 00:43:46,202
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

834
00:43:48,051 --> 00:43:52,442
♪I valued all but indifferent
to wealth and fame♪

835
00:43:53,978 --> 00:43:59,451
♪Basking in the sun,
I couldn't feel your sunlight♪

836
00:44:00,402 --> 00:44:06,234
♪All I feel is a painful heat wave♪

837
00:44:09,082 --> 00:44:13,818
♪All things are dim,
while only your eyes shine bright♪

838
00:44:15,130 --> 00:44:19,642
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

839
00:44:21,082 --> 00:44:27,034
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

840
00:44:27,811 --> 00:44:32,122
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

841
00:44:33,114 --> 00:44:38,080
♪You came with wind and rain,
while left with my four seasons♪

842
00:44:39,072 --> 00:44:43,680
♪All is bleak without you♪

843
00:44:45,018 --> 00:44:50,624
♪It began like a tornado,
and went away leaving only dust♪

844
00:44:51,738 --> 00:45:02,752
♪Without you,
even the most beautiful world is a mess♪
